"7 teaspoons canola oil, divided","3/4 cup finely chopped onion","1/2 cup finely chopped peeled carrot","3  garlic cloves, minced","3/4 cup water","1/3 cup uncooked quinoa","1/2 cup panko","1/2 teaspoon kosher salt","1/2 teaspoon freshly ground black pepper","1 1/2 cups canned unsalted chickpeas, rinsed and drained","1  large egg","2 tablespoons hot sauce (such as Tabasco)","4  (1 1/2-ounce) whole-wheat hamburger buns, toasted","4  romaine lettuce leaves","4  (1/4-inch-thick) slices tomato"